    "body": "A more minimal demonstration is\n\n```\nimport grpc\n\n\nclass ClassWithMutableClassScopeState(object):\n    channel = None\n\n\ndef test_leak():\n    channel = grpc.secure_channel(\n        'bigtable.googleapis.com:443', grpc.ssl_channel_credentials())\n    ClassWithMutableClassScopeState.channel = channel\n    grpc.channel_ready_future(channel).result()\n```\n\n. I was surprised by how the problem requires execution by `nosetests`; just running the code with `python` isn't enough. As I suspected, the problem manifests on with `grpcio` 1.0.0 but not with master.\n\nHow severely are you affected? How much of a problem would it be to wait for the fix in `grpcio` 1.1?\n"
  },
