    "body": "@nathanielmanistaatgoogle You already [provided one](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/7849#issuecomment-242567436), except you left out the `if __name__ == '__main__'` part. I [added](https://gist.github.com/dhermes/5c1fbeda25ffc26d31b890a10e551aa2) the `__main__` part as well as an env. var. to turn off leaking and [dropped it in a gist](https://gist.github.com/dhermes/5c1fbeda25ffc26d31b890a10e551aa2).\n\n```\n$ LEAK=False python leak_example.py\n$ LEAK=True python leak_example.py\nE1018 09:42:38.499929680   25706 network_status_tracker.c:48] Memory leaked as all network endpoints were not shut down\n```\n"
