    "updated_at": "2016-11-15T16:16:04Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The fix for this has not yet been released and the min repro is probably sufficient but I haven't yet found time to confirm.\n\nSince we believe this is fixed in gRPC Python 1.1-and-later (by [this change](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/7538) by @thunderboltsid), and since we believe that gRPC Python 1.1 will appear sometime before the end of the year, we haven't had much reason of our own to take the time to look into this. This issue doesn't yet have a priority label on it - while it's not high-priority for us, is it high-priority for you? How hot should we consider this fire to be burning?\n"
  },
