    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "> How hot should we consider this fire to be burning?\n\nVery hot? Most users end up seeing this error, and many of them are using `google-cloud-python` or GAX-generated libraries. So they go from not even **knowing** they were using gRPC to finding out that gRPC is leaking memory (and causing program shutdown to hang for 2-5 seconds).\n\n@jonparrott WDYT?\n"
